original: Kirudd, Elsa Gunborg Kristina, fil. mag., Borås, f. 10/2/08 i Jukkasjärvi, Norrb. 1., av groisshandl. Bror K. o. Sofia Eriksson. — Studiex. i Uddevalla 28, fri. mag. 33, provår i Sthlm 41-42. Res. t. Tyskl. 34, 37 o. 39. E. lär. i Uddevalla 36, Skara 36-41, Norrmalms flicksk. i Sthlm 41-42 o. 42-43, Västerås 43-44, e. o. adj. i Jönköp. 44-45, adj. i modersm. o. tyska v. Borås h. a. 1. sed. 45.
translated: Kirudd, Elsa Gunborg Kristina, Master of Arts, Borås, b. 10/2/08 in Jukkasjärvi, Norrbotten County, eldest daughter of wholesale merchant Bror K. and Sofia Eriksson. — Completed upper secondary education in Uddevalla in 1928, graduated with a Master's degree in 1933, spent an additional year studying in Stockholm from 1941-1942. Traveled to Germany in 1934, 1937, and 1939. Employed as a teacher in Uddevalla from 1936, in Skara from 1936-1941, at Norrmalms girls' school in Stockholm from 1941-1942 and 1942-1943, in Västerås from 1943-1944, served as substitute teacher in Jönköping in 1944-1945, and has been a permanent teacher of mother tongue and German at Borås high school since 1945.
